snippet.title: Pinball/Flipper - Interton VC 4000 # 23
snippet.description: A tiny flipper game for the Interton console. Great ball physics, but lousy board layout. Can be a lot of fun, but alså quite frustrating at times. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2013/05/pinballflipper-vc-4000.html
